border:none;padding:0cm'><a name="4920781-5139902-2_22"></a><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:black;font-weight:normal'>第十八条</span></h3>

</div>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:19.5pt;background:white'><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;color:black'>中国工会全国代表大会的职权是：</span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:19.5pt;background:white'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:black'>(</span><span
