style='font-family:宋体;color:black;font-weight:normal'>第三十八条</span></h3>

</div>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:19.5pt;background:white'><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;color:black'>工会资产是社会团体资产，中华全国总工会对各级工会的资产拥有终极所有权。根据经费独立原则，建立预算、决算、资产监管和经费审查监督制度。实行</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:black'>“</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;color:black'>统一领导、分级管理</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:black'>”</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;color:black'>的财务体制、</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:black'>“</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;color:black'>统一所有、分级监管、单位使用</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:black'>”</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;color:black'>的资产监管体制和</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:black'>“</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;color:black'>统一领导、分级管理、分级负责</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:black'>”</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;color:black'>的经费审查监督体制。工会经费、资产的管理和使用办法以及工会经费审查监督制度，由中华全国总工会制定。</span></p>

